    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Some files produces warnings while they are loaded using Zend_Search_Lucene_Document_Html class.</p>

<p>That's actually PHP bug (just registered as <a href="http://bugs.php.net/46159">PHP bug #46159</a>).</p>

<p>Workarownd:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
DOMDocument::loadHTMLFile($fname);
</code></pre>

<p>==&gt;</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$htmlData = file_get_contents($fname);
DOMDocument::loadHTML($htmlData);
</code></pre>

